 reserved chopped ginger and reserved clementine juice then mix <b>20 sec\/speed 3<b>. Mix well with spatula."},{"content":"Divide batter between pudding basins, filling them ¾ full. Cover desserts with prepared baking paper circles, buttered side down and push mixture down a little. Cover each pudding basin with foil or baking paper, secure with string or an elastic band and place into Varoma dish. Clean and dry mixing bowl."},{"content":"Place water in mixing bowl then place Varoma into position. Steam <b>40 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Serve warm with cream (if using)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Serve with homemade custard (see recipe in <em>The Basic Cookbook<\/em>) instead of cream if preferred."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h","4 portions"]}